title: Ariana Grande - Unreleased
description: Grande possesses a four octave light lyric soprano vocal range. She has been deemed the "mini Mariah Carey" and the "new Mariah Carey" by critics due to her wide vocal range. Grande expressed her feelings towards being compared to Mariah Carey as a "huge compliment" and a "blessing",and often cites both Carey and Houston as influences for her work. In another interview, she said: "I mean, it's a huge compliment, but when you hear my entire album, you'll see that Mariah's sound is much different than mine." Her music is generally pop and R&B, and has elements of funk, dance, and hip hop.She grew up mainly listening to urban pop and 90s music. DJ Jeff Duran Puts together a special mix of her unreleased and cover songs.
